olive oil
1 bag Asian Stir-Fry Mix
1 packet beef strips
1 sachet Southeast Asian Spice Blend
1 packet udon noodles
1 bunch herbs
1 packet Sichuan garlic paste
1 packet Crispy Shallots
1 packet garlic paste

Heat olive oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat.
Cook stir-fry mix until softened, 3 mins.
Transfer to a bowl and set aside.
Return pan to high heat. Cook beef, spice blend and garlic paste, tossing, until browned, 1-2 mins.

Meanwhile, pierce noodle packet and zap in the microwave until steaming, 2 mins.
Roughly chop herbs.

Now, add Sichuan paste, noodles and stir-fry mix to the beef.
Season and stir.
Divide between plates and top with crispy shallots and herbs.